name: Global Killing: Awakening SSS-Level Talent at the Beginning!
author: 漫潮社
content: Using Bing translation:Violent start, SSS level talent awakening! Tens of billions of people from all over the world, at the same time, descended on the heavens to kill the world. Hundreds of countries such as the Lighthouse Kingdom, the Dragon Kingdom, and the Sakurajima Kingdom are competing! Di Si Qin Feng woke up the SSS level talent at the beginning - Endless Extraction! He can extract everything! Including extracting demons! Turn on Infinite Kill Mode!
